    "purpose": "RewardXtra ka 'brain' — India ke top cards ki reward rules. Recommender ise padh kar best card rank karta hai.",
    "howRankingWorks": "Diye gaye category + amount pe: har card ke liye matching rule ka effectiveRate lo (agar category exclusions mein hai to 0), value = amount * effectiveRate/100, monthlyCapValue se cap karo, phir cards ko value ke hisaab se rank karo.",
    "effectiveRate": "Sab kuch ek hi unit (%) mein normalize kiya hai taaki cashback/points/miles cards directly compare ho saken. Points/miles cards ke liye effectiveRate = (reward per rupee) * pointValueINR * 100, conservative pointValue ke saath. Asli raw rule 'rawRate' mein transparency ke liye rakhi hai.",
    "monthlyCapValue": "Reward value ka monthly cap RUPEES mein (cashback-equivalent). null = no cap / unlimited.",
    "assumptions": "Points/mile values redemption pe depend karte hain; humne conservative average liya hai. Reward rules banks frequently change karte hain — 'lastVerified' aur SOURCES.md check karein."
  },
